it.emarolab.sit

Interface SITBase.DATA_PROPERTY

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SITBase.VOCABOLARY
    Enclosing interface:
    SITBase

    public static interface SITBase.DATA_PROPERTY
extends SITBase.VOCABOLARY
    The interface containing all the constants related to data properties.

    This interface is aimed to be a container for all the String constants used in the ontology for addressing data properties.
    All related values should be expressed in meters.

    File: it.emarolab.sit.SITBase
    Licence: GNU GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE. Version 3, 29 June 2007
    Author: Buoncompagni Luca (luca.buoncompagni@edu.unige.it)
    affiliation: EMAROLab, DIBRIS, University of Genoa.
    date: 05/06/17
